{{flavour|A magical healing elixir which causes wounds to close and heal almost instantly.}}

[[Quaff]]ing a '''potion of heal wounds''' restores <code>9 + 3d28/3</code> [[HP]]<ref>{{source ref|0.30.1|potion.cc|208}}</ref> (10-37 HP, 23 HP on average), up to your max HP. 

{{crawlquote|You feel much better.}}

Unlike a [[potion of curing]], potions of heal wounds do not cure [[status effects]] ([[poison]] or [[confusion]]), but the restored HP may keep you alive long enough for them to pass on their own.

==History==
*Prior to [[0.26]], this potion could restore [[rot]]ted HP.
*Prior to [[0.17]], potions of heal wounds could only heal rot damage at or near full health.

